distraction: There was no way you could do anything during this study. It was a very interesting study; but sometimes it went too fast for this 73 year old mind to grasp. But it was fun.
strategies: I tried to remember the pictures; but after a while; they all seemed to go with each other. The last task was very hard. I thought they all went together.
easier: I think the first task was the easiest because the next two were much harder. I thought my mind would pick up on the pictures while I stared at the cross and tried to do the colors. I was wrong. It didn't work out the way I thought it would.
similar: No; I never did a study like this one.
comments: It was NOT boring that's for sure!
